# TodoExample

Example Todo list application written in Flex using the latest version of Robotlegs.

## Specification

* User can add a task to the todo list.
* User can delete an existing task from the todo list.
* User can modify an existing task from the todo list.
* User is presented a message notify that there are no tasks when the todo list is empty.
* User is given feedback when adding, modifying or deleting an item from the todo list.
* User can't enter a task that has no text.